-- Valeant, Ackman to submit Allergan special meeting request-CNBC
-- By Caroline Humer
-- Fri Aug 22, 2014 10:01AM EDT
-- None



Aug 22 (Reuters) - Valeant Pharmaceuticals International Inc <VRX.TO> and Pershing Square Capital Management will submit a request on Friday to Allergan Inc <AGN.N> for a special shareholders meeting, sources told CNBC television.

Allergan's corporate bylaws require Valeant and Pershing Square to have more than 25 percent of shareholders' votes in favor of holding the meeting. They have support from more than 30 percent, CNBC reported, citing the sources.